    "local_director_required": true,
    "note_md": {
      "en": "ACRA states foreigners must use a Corporate Service Provider, meet local residency requirements, and have at least one local resident. Entrepreneurs with venture-backed or innovative-tech companies can apply for EntrePass before incorporation or within six months of setup.",
      "zh-Hans": "ACRA 规定外国人必须使用企业服务提供商、满足当地居住要求，并且至少拥有一名当地居民。拥有风投支持或创新科技公司的企业家可以在公司成立前或成立后六个月内申请创业准证。"
    }
  },
