      "en": "Family passes require business-spending and local-workforce thresholds. MOM lists Dependant's Pass for a legally married spouse and unmarried children under 21, and Long-Term Visit Pass routes for common-law spouses, certain children, and parents.",
      "zh-Hans": "家属准证需要商业支出和当地劳动力门槛。 MOM 列出了针对合法结婚配偶和 21 岁以下未婚子女的家属准证，以及针对同居配偶、某些子女和父母的长期访问准证途径。"
